O        0.000000000   0.000000000   0.500000000
O        0.500000000   0.500000000   0.500000000
Pb       0.500000000   0.000000000   0.450000000
Pb       0.000000000   0.500000000   0.550000000
K_POINTS {automatic}
8 8 1 1 1 0
CELL_PARAMETERS (angstrom)
   3.900000000   0.000000000   0.000000000
   0.000000000   3.900000000   0.000000000
   0.000000000   0.000000000  20.000000000